import React from "react";
import {
  FooterContainer,
  FooterWrap,
  FooterLinksContainer,
  FooterLinksWrapper,
  FooterLinkItems,
  FooterLinkTitle,
  FooterLink,
  SocialMedia,
  SocialMediaWrap,
  SocialLogo,
  SocialIcons,
  SocialIconLinks,
  WebsiteRights,
} from "./FooterElements";

const Footer = () => {
  return (
    <FooterContainer>
      <FooterWrap>
        <FooterLinksContainer>
          <FooterLinksWrapper>
            <FooterLinkItems>
              <FooterLinkTitle>About us</FooterLinkTitle>
              <FooterLink to="/signin">About us</FooterLink>
              <FooterLink to="/signin">How it works</FooterLink>
              <FooterLink to="/signin">Testomonialys</FooterLink>
              <FooterLink to="/signin">Carrers</FooterLink>
              <FooterLink to="/signin">Investors</FooterLink>
              <FooterLink to="/signin">Terms of Service</FooterLink>
            </FooterLinkItems>
            <FooterLinkItems>
              <FooterLinkTitle>Contact us</FooterLinkTitle>
              <FooterLink to="/signin">Contact</FooterLink>
              <FooterLink to="/signin">Support</FooterLink>
              <FooterLink to="/signin">Destination</FooterLink>
              <FooterLink to="/signin">Sponsorship</FooterLink>
            </FooterLinkItems>
          </FooterLinksWrapper>
          <FooterLinksWrapper>
            <FooterLinkItems>
              <FooterLinkTitle>Videos</FooterLinkTitle>
              <FooterLink to="/signin">Submit Video</FooterLink>
              <FooterLink to="/signin">Ambassadors</FooterLink>
              <FooterLink to="/signin">Agency</FooterLink>
              <FooterLink to="/signin">Influencer</FooterLink>
            </FooterLinkItems>
            <FooterLinkItems>
              <FooterLinkTitle>Social Media</FooterLinkTitle>
              <FooterLink to="/signin">Instagram</FooterLink>
              <FooterLink to="/signin">Facebook</FooterLink>
              <FooterLink to="/signin">Youtube</FooterLink>
              <FooterLink to="/signin">Twitter</FooterLink>
            </FooterLinkItems>
          </FooterLinksWrapper>
        </FooterLinksContainer>
        <SocialMedia>
          <SocialMediaWrap>
            <SocialLogo to="/">dataSpec</SocialLogo>
            <WebsiteRights>dataSpec © 2021 AlL rights reserved.</WebsiteRights>
            <SocialIcons>
              <SocialIconsLinks href="/" traget="_blank" aria-label="Facebook">
                <FaFacebook />
              </SocialIconsLinks>
              <SocialIconsLinks href="/" traget="_blank" aria-label="Instagram">
                <FaInstagram />
              </SocialIconsLinks>
              <SocialIconsLinks href="/" traget="_blank" aria-label="Twitter">
                <FaTwitter />
              </SocialIconsLinks>
              <SocialIconsLinks href="//www.youtube.com" traget="_blank" aria-label="Youtube">
                <FaYoutube />
              </SocialIconsLinks>
              <SocialIconsLinks href="/" traget="_blank" aria-label="LinkedIn">
                <FaLinkedIn />
              </SocialIconsLinks>
            </SocialIcons>
          </SocialMediaWrap>
        </SocialMedia>
      </FooterWrap>
    </FooterContainer>
  );
};

export default Footer;
